{
  "stem": "107.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- he had some interest in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know him as well as one of the people standing there when he comes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had never anything to do with me, or I had never anything to do with him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was cold like ice, and he assumed-- I am sure he assumed what he was doing was in the interest of the movement of creating a big, German, powerful, imperial, with no foreign blood, which is a strange concept-- would find any rights or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say always that he was totally detached.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, when he puts this psychotic, the manic patient, who was a lovely young man, send him to be executed, that was just like you sent another patient for surgery.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no particular-- I mean, I have never seen him [INAUDIBLE] with newcomers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I have seen pictures, and I know and have listened to people who where there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- he did it as a duty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is no excuse, of course, but of course he was also very clever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He knew how to save himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm sure he had a fortune of-- of gold and money stolen from the people who arrived in Auschwitz, sent to Switzerland or wherever, and when he went to South America-- but I mean this--",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, first of all, there was a gypsy camp, but that-- I got in touch with this a little later.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In summer of '44, we are still in our hospital in the Czech family camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, cannot be.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let me think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the disaster was in March, so it must have started before-- came the mass transportations from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Hungarian Jews somehow survived until the last year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I thought it was '44, but it somehow doesn't figure out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No, it was '44 because I was back to the hospital, of course.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was '44.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were selected-- only the younger people were put into a camp, and the others went straight into the gas chambers-- 10 thousands of people still in relatively good shape because they had to eat in Hungary not everything, but enough to survive and-- and had still a more or less normal life until the Germans took over and just started these transportations.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There's a camp next to us which at the time was empty prior to the arrival of the Hungarian Jews, which was made into a camp of young women, which were then supposed to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And these young women had lost everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were shorn.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had no hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had nothing of their original clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They got little summer dresses that they had collected from others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They're freezing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The nights were still very cold, and were totally confused.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't know what's happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They had no warning, no understanding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We, at least, had rumors which we could put together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Some of them were very young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They came to-- there was an electrically charged fence between the two camps-- our hospital camp and that Hungarian camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They came as close as they could come, and there were some difficulties in communications.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were a few that talked a little bit Slovak, and we usually talked Czech so we could communicate, but more or less we communicate by movement, gesture.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was a one-- I take out from many little tragedies I saw that is girls, where a small number of survivors from a big transport that was selected-- the chimneys were smoking all the time, and this is-- it was a hectic time, a terrible time.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They didn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They didn't want to believe it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, one of these girls spoke a little German and explained to me that while she was sent to the washroom, which really was a washroom, the other washrooms were gas chambers-- was raped by one of the SS people.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A really beautiful-- even shorn and desperate-- young woman, and she thought that this was the worst thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had never had any contact with a man, and that was the worst thing that can happen to her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she was in pain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had some aspirin in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We throw it over the-- some aspirin over the fence, some aspirin, and talked to her, and she says I wonder if he comes again?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, the greatest fear like in rape traumatized young woman is, what if it happens again?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I told her what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said you just make yourself as tall as you can be and don't look at him, or she wouldn't even know that it was he or any of the-- just look into the emptiness.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Ignore, but don't face.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't confront.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You look like any one looks.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
